<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="57" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1436,151,716]" pageId="16" pageNumber="57">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,331,548,572]" pageId="16" pageNumber="57">Etymology.</emphasis>
From the Greek 
<taxonomicName box="[524,617,548,572]" class="Insecta" family="Mutillidae" genus="Tobantilla" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Metazoa" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kolasma">
<emphasis box="[524,617,548,572]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="57">kolasma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
“punishment”, a noun in apposition. This species, along with 
<taxonomicName box="[1317,1408,548,572]" class="Insecta" family="Mutillidae" genus="Tobantilla" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Metazoa" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="krima">
<emphasis box="[1317,1408,548,572]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="57">T. krima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is named after the Russian novel Преступление и наказание “Crime and Punishment” written by Fyodor Mikhailovich Dostoevsky.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="57" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1436,151,716]" pageId="16" pageNumber="57">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,313,656,680]" pageId="16" pageNumber="57">Remarks.</emphasis>
The scutellar scale of this species is similar to that of 
<taxonomicName box="[929,1055,656,680]" class="Insecta" family="Mutillidae" genus="Lomachaeta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="frigidula">
<emphasis box="[929,1055,656,680]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="57">T. frigidula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This species also has a narrower pygidial plate than 
<taxonomicName box="[366,458,692,716]" class="Insecta" family="Mutillidae" genus="Tobantilla" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Metazoa" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="krima">
<emphasis box="[366,458,692,716]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="57">T. krima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and the Argentinean 
<taxonomicName box="[700,814,692,716]" class="Insecta" family="Mutillidae" genus="Tobantilla" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Metazoa" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[700,814,692,716]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="57">Tobantilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species.
</paragraph>
